e is resolved.\",\n163:         \"targetBehavior\": \"Phase 1 preserves the startup foundation with `EntryAbility` lifecycle hooks, main-window loading, and direct inspection of the persisted login flag, but does not yet render the final onboarding/home route split before page composition.\",\n164:         \"notes\": \"Simplified startup lifecycle parity; full user-visible route gating is deferred to phase 2 per plan.\"\n165:       },\n166:       \"append\": {\n167:         \"targetEndpoints\": [\n168:           \"entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onCreate\",\n169:           \"entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onWindowStageCreate\",\n170:           \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/startup/startup_store.cj::resolveStartRoute\"\n171:         ],\n172:         \"verificationEvidence\": [\n173:           \"Source inspection: app/build.gradle.kts enables compose=true and adds androidx.core.splashscreen.\",\n174:           \"Target inspection: app_ability.cj reads persisted login state during onCreate and bootstrap page loading still compiles in the phase build gate.\"\n175:         ]\n176:       }\n177:     },\n178:     {\n179:       \"featureId\": \"app-build-gradle-kts-aa010bdd3d-005-settings-preferences-option-toggles-or-c\",\n180:       \"set\": {\n181:         \"status\": \"implemented\",\n182:         \"parityLevel\": \"equivalent\",\n183:         \"sourceBehavior\": \"`app/build.gradle.kts` includes DataStore Preferences as the app's lightweight persisted configuration/session dependency.\",\n184:         \"targetBehavior\": \"`login_preferences_service.cj` preserves that lightweight persisted session boundary with HarmonyOS `Preferences` file/key constants and read/toggle methods for the login flag.\",\n185:         \"notes\": \"Phase 1 closes the persisted preference service boundary even though later phases will wire more UI mutations to it.\"\n186:       },\n187:       \"append\": {\n188:         \"tar